      "pos": [
        8719,
        8799
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "When you create virtual machine using one of those images, you’ll need to provide a user name and password, which you’ll use to log on to the virtual machine.",
      "pos": [
        8800,
        8958
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "If you’ve forgotten the user name or password and you’ve installed the VM Agent, you can install and use the VMAccess extension to fix the problem.",
