      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Azure Backup is available as a preview in certain regions.",
      "pos": [
        10880,
        10938
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "For details, see <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>Back up Azure virtual machines<ept id=\"p1\">](backup-azure-vms.md)</ept>.",
      "pos": [
        10939,
        11010
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Other solutions are available from certified partners.",
